{"tid":686880,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次拍拖..但男朋友係住劏房..","createTime":"2018-06-01T16:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T10:36:17.000Z","uid":29540,"like":1,"dislike":88,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"efacc9a6e1163ad7613b0d05871d3344f212e1ed","tid":686880,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T16:37:12.000Z","msg":"今次係我第一次拍拖..因為男朋友幾高大靚仔, 學識又高 , 講野都斯斯文文 , 但拍左兩個月之後 , 我話諗住去佢屋企玩（其實大家都明想做咩） , 點知佢唔肯 , 我就好奇怪 ,  點解送上門都唔要? 問左佢好多次 , 最後搞到我發脾氣佢先肯坦白 , 原來佢同屋企人罵左架 , 而家係住緊深水埗果d一百尺既劏房...<br />\n<br />\n連一個人生活都成問題 , 仲點帶我上去玩 , 其實聽到既時候我真係嚇左跳 ,  我自己家景雖然唔算好 , 但都算七八百尺 , 一家三口加一隻狗 , 真係冇諗過竟然有差唔多年紀既人會住咁細既地方...而家好大打擊 , 都唔知同佢繼續一唔一齊好..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97568b881502fb5329deffd265fe45f36bf988ce","tid":686880,"uid":21423,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T16:37:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb60d8a81600501f6cf3d009b39c20f30b968e3c","tid":686880,"uid":184374,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T16:39:13.000Z","msg":"拍拖兩個月就自動送上門比人破處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c29175889602b83144b32a616f6b63829a57a79","tid":686880,"uid":59569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T16:40:13.000Z","msg":"7分"},{"pid":"08638bee30c6b37eda895d7b3933f933a87afd8a","tid":686880,"uid":179547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T16:41:20.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23416b60ce3342a6eaf9faad9bc7a09434216255","tid":686880,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T16:41:24.000Z","msg":"又係邊到抄番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49fd0168860695a2e5acce8950fe505417cb04d0","tid":686880,"uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T16:41:57.000Z","msg":"包養埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/no